new representation of the\ncommunication constraint. This approach allows us to strengthen and generalize\nexisting results with simpler and more transparent proofs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Feb 2018 07:34:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2018 23:22:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 15 Sep 2020 08:53:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 22 Jul 2021 09:55:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-23"}
